<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <title>Your OTP Code</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        background-color: #0b0b14;
        color: #f0ede6;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
      }

      .container {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 60px auto;
        background: #0e0e1a;
        padding: 32px;
        border-radius: 16px;
        box-shadow: 0 24px 80px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
        border: 1px solid #1e1e2e;
      }

      .logo {
        text-align: center;
        font-size: 20px;
        font-weight: 800;
        letter-spacing: 1px;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
        background: linear-gradient(90deg, #f0c96b, #c9973a);
        -webkit-background-clip: text;
        -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
      }

      h2 {
        color: #f0c96b;
        margin-bottom: 10px;
      }

      p {
        color: #8a8498;
        line-height: 1.6;
        font-size: 14px;
      }

      .otp-box {
        margin: 25px 0;
        padding: 18px;
        text-align: center;
        font-size: 26px;
        font-weight: bold;
        letter-spacing: 10px;
        background: #08080f;
        border: 1px solid #c9973a44;
        border-radius: 12px;
        color: #f0c96b;
        font-family: monospace;
      }

      .highlight {
        color: #c9973a;
        font-weight: 700;
      }

      .note {
        margin-top: 20px;
        font-size: 12px;
        color: #6b6478;
      }

      .footer {
        margin-top: 30px;
        text-align: center;
        font-size: 12px;
        color: #3a3650;
        border-top: 1px solid #1e1e2e;
        padding-top: 15px;
      }

      .brand {
        font-weight: 700;
        background: linear-gradient(90deg, #f0c96b, #c9973a);
        -webkit-background-clip: text;
        -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
      }
    </style>
  </head>

  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="logo">Task Management System</div>

      <h2>Verify Your Account</h2>

      <p>
        Use the following OTP code to verify your account. Please enter it in
        the verification screen.
      </p>

      <div class="otp-box"><%= otp %></div>

      <p>This code will expire in <span class="highlight">10 minutes</span>.</p>

      <p>If you didn’t request this code, you can safely ignore this email.</p>

      <div class="note">Security tip: Never share this code with anyone.</div>

      <div class="footer">
        &copy; <%= year %> <span class="brand">Task Management System</span>. All rights
        reserved.
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
